description: Thank You for stopping at our store! Our decals can be applied on any clean, flat, smooth, light-textured surface, such as walls, windows, tiles, floors, furniture, tv, computers, cars, etc. Our decals are made of high-quality vinyl and look great on any surface indoors and outdoors (please let us know if you want us to use outdoor vinyl). They are easy to apply and you can remove them without damaging the wall. They are removable but not reusable. The decal is one solid color so the color of the background will be the color of your surface. Decals don't have transparent tape that's why they look like a hand painting. We can customize decals and can make different sizes just contact us first! Product made in the USA.
